<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===Trust boost===
Supporters receive an increase in their [[Special:MyLanguage/Trust Rank|Trust Rank]]. This boost can elevate a user's trust rank to the next level. The minimum Trust Rank received is User, which is particularly beneficial for newcomers who want to start content creation immediately.
If already a User or Known rank, the trust boost is unlikely to have an immediate effect. For those with a Trusted rank, the boost will have no effect.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===Age Verification===
[[Special:MyLanguage/Age Verification|Age Verification]] is a feature accessible to VRC+ subscribers with a [[VRChat account]], allowing users to verify their age. This grants a special marker that can be displayed on their profile and nameplate, as well as access or host to age restricted [[Special:MyLanguage/Groups|Group]] instances for users 18 and over.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===Camera===
An active VRC+ subscription adds two major features related to the camera.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
====Camera Dolly====
[[Special:MyLanguage/Camera Dolly|Camera Dolly]] is a VRC+-exclusive camera system designed for advanced users. This feature allows users to create and play animations for the VRChat [[Special:MyLanguage/Camera|camera]].
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
====Camera Drone====
[[Special:MyLanguage/Camera Drone|Camera Drone]] is a VRC+-exclusive feature that allows users to spawn and fly around a fully-functional drone.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Other features===
[[File:SupporterBadge.png|thumb|120x120px|The "Supporter" badge, displayed on a subscriber's profile]]
Additional features include:
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
*'''Instance naming''' - When creating an [[Special:MyLanguage/Instances#Instance naming|instance]], VRC+ supporters have the option to name it.
*'''Shop discounts''' - VRC+ supporters have the option to purchase [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|shop]] listings for a discount.
*'''VRC+ Supporter [[Special:MyLanguage/Badges|Badge]]''' - Being an active supporter of VRC+ will grant a user a "Supporter" badge, as long as their subscription is active. This special badge can be found on your user profile on the platform, and on the VRChat website.
*'''VRC+ [[Badges#VRC+ Tenure badges|Tenure Badge]]''' - Being an active supporter of VRC+ will grant a user a "VRC+ Subscriber" badge, as long as their subscription is active, this badge shows the user's cumulative duration of them being subscribed to VRC+.
*'''VRCat on Quick Menu''' - Clickable VRCat on top of Quick Menu that makes sounds and displays different prompts.
*'''Clock variant''' - Access to use the "VRChat+ Ultra Premium Time ☆" [[Special:MyLanguage/Quick Menu#Clock|clock]] variant.
*'''Reduced display name change cooldown''' - Changing display name will be reduced to 30 days from the normal 90-day cooldown.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Features that were available to supporters, but are no longer available to new supporters:
</div> 

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
*'''Early Supporter Badge'''
*'''VRChat for Android Mobile Early Access'''
*'''Stickers'''
*'''Selfie Expression on PC'''
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Purchasing==
VRC+ can only be purchased in-client through the VRC+ tab at the bottom right of the [[Special:MyLanguage/Quick Menu|Quick Menu]], and [[Special:MyLanguage/Main Menu|Main Menu]]. VRC+ is available on Steam, Meta Quest Store, Pico, Google Play, and iOS devices.
</div>

