<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===Technical information===
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
====Using VRC+ on different platforms====
Subscription payments are processed through platform partners (Steam or Meta). Contact their support for payment-related issues. You can purchase VRC+ on Steam even if you primarily use another platform, like Oculus PC, by merging your Oculus PC account into your VRChat account.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
====Subscription issues====
For issues with VRC+ features, contact VRChat Support. Subscription payments are processed through platform partners (Steam or Meta), so contact their support services for payment issues. Refunds for subscriptions are not permitted by the platforms; VRChat does not offer refunds after purchase.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
====Subscription renewal and lapse ====
When a VRC+ subscription lapses:
*Custom inventory content is saved but becomes inaccessible until the subscription is renewed.
**Your custom user icon will be unequipped.
*Avatar favorite lists will be saved, but not accessible.
**Access to favorite list 1 will be accessible.
*Badges and Trust boost gained from VRC+ are retained. 
**The Supporter & VRC+ Tenure badges will be removed. The badges progress are saved and will be added back when resubscribed.
*Other VRC+ features will be disabled, with data saved for future access if the subscription is restarted.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
====Canceling VRC+ subscription====
'''Steam:'''
1. Visit the Steam Account Details page.
2. Click “Manage Subscriptions.”
3. Cancel or renew subscriptions as needed.
</div> 

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
For more details, see the [https://help.steampowered.com/en/faqs/view/726E-E811-168F-0D9E Steam Support article on recurring subscriptions].
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
'''Meta Quest Store:'''
1. In your Meta Quest headset, select “Your Account” in the Store left sidebar.
2. Select “Subscriptions,” then “VRChat,” and finally “Cancel Subscription.”
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Gifting VRC+ ==
VRC+ can be gifted to other users. If a user already has an active subscription, gifting them will extend its duration.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
To gift a user with VRC+, you can click on them if they are in the same instance as you, and click '''Gift VRC+'''. You can also search for a user in either the '''Search''' tab, or '''Social''' tab, and also click '''Gift VRC+''' when on their profile.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===<span id="Gift drop"></span>Gift drop===
You can visually gift several users in an instance simultaneously, by using a gift drop. If the number of gifts exceeds the number of users in the instance, some users may receive multiple months of VRC+
</div> 

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
When dropping gifts, you can choose to either distribute them equally among users in the instance, or to prioritize dropping to the closest users. Gift drop bundles must be consumed in a single drop and cannot be used partially or split.
</div> 

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Gift drops may include discounts of up to 50%.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==== Quantity and pricing for gift drops====
Users can purchase a bundle of VRC+ subscriptions to drop. Each bundle represents a number of one-month VRC+ subscriptions. For example, the ‘10’ bundle grants ten one-month subscriptions to users in the instance.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Purchasing the bundle of 5 saves 5% of the regular cost; bundle of 10 saves 10%, bundle of 20 saves 25%, bundle of 50 saves 35%, and the bundle of 100 subscriptions saves 50%.
